{EAST has 17 points and might open 1NT. But with the 5-card Major suit she prefers

to open 1♠.

WEST has good ♠ support and 10 points, counting 1 for the doubleton ♣.

It is easily worth a raise to 2♠

EAST cannot bid game yet, after all, WEST could have as few as 6 points. But she can

continue with a 3♠ bid in hopes that WEST actually has 9 or 10 points.

WEST comes through with 4♠.}
